   <narrative xml:lang="EN">HFC Phase Down Plan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Following the outcomes of the 87th Meeting of the Executive Committee of the Multilateral Fund for the Implementation of the Montreal Protocol and subsequently Decision 87/??(c), funding was approved for Albania for the preparation of Kigali HFC implementation plans. Legal documents, stakeholder engagement, and awareness raising events have been completed in the project, which led to the ratification of the Kigali Amendment on 18 January 2019. Albania has collected preliminary data for HFC for some years. The HFC related legal framework and its implementation for licensing the import and export of new, used, recycled and reclaimed HFC will be put into place by January 2021</narrative>
  </description>
